(Xu Lvyang's Moments)

1970
01:19:38,520 --> 01:19:39,800
It's a statement of my stance.

1971
01:19:39,800 --> 01:19:42,120
Apart from apologizing in person,

1972
01:19:42,120 --> 01:19:42,960
