1974
01:19:48,200 --> 01:19:50,360
From now on, I will follow my heart.

1975
01:19:50,360 --> 01:19:52,040
I hope nothing I do

1976
01:19:52,040 --> 01:19:54,480
will hurt anyone,

1977
01:19:54,480 --> 01:19:55,040
and

1978
01:19:55,040 --> 01:19:56,440
it would be ideal

1979
01:19:56,440 --> 01:19:57,280
