1999
01:20:34,600 --> 01:20:35,720
Wasn't it "sky and earth"?

2000
01:20:36,120 --> 01:20:38,040
(Some rejoice while others grieve.)

2001
01:20:38,320 --> 01:20:39,440
We just went through

2002
01:20:39,440 --> 01:20:40,240
who checked

2003
