2004
01:20:41,480 --> 01:20:43,000
Any surprises?

2005
01:20:43,000 --> 01:20:44,560
Ling Lizheng is so direct.

2006
01:20:44,560 --> 01:20:45,040
Yes.

2007
01:20:45,240 --> 01:20:46,600
I have a special feeling.

2008
01:20:46,600 --> 01:20:47,480
I think

2009
01:20:47,480 --> 01:20:48,400
when we see Ling Lizheng,

2010
01:20:48,400 --> 01:20:49,520
we will find that

2011
01:20:49,520 --> 01:20:50,360
a person's appearance

2012
