2017
01:20:57,320 --> 01:20:59,000
But once you're firmly chosen,

2018
01:20:59,000 --> 01:20:59,400
you will

2019
01:20:59,400 --> 01:21:00,400
instantly

2020
01:21:00,400 --> 01:21:01,480
