That's exactly what loving someone
feels like.

2037
01:21:24,560 --> 01:21:25,120
Yes.

2038
01:21:25,120 --> 01:21:26,760
Actually, in a romantic relationship,

2039
01:21:26,760 --> 01:21:27,880
