2044
01:21:32,520 --> 01:21:35,040
I used to struggle badly
with appearance anxiety.

2045
01:21:35,040 --> 01:21:36,120
When I started acting,

2046
01:21:36,120 --> 01:21:36,640
I realized that

2047
