2053
01:21:45,720 --> 01:21:47,440
I have strengths in other areas,

2054
01:21:47,440 --> 01:21:48,280
and even my flaws

2055
01:21:48,280 --> 01:21:50,040
can be as beautiful as stars.

2056
01:21:50,040 --> 01:21:50,360
Right.

2057
01:21:50,360 --> 01:21:50,960
So I think

2058
01:21:50,960 --> 01:21:52,240
the sun and stars

2059
01:21:52,240 --> 01:21:53,600
make up day and night,

2060
01:21:53,600 --> 01:21:55,280
